('FIXED', 'marine', '', 'BSOS12F20I66', 'Marine fixed fisheye camera - stainless steel construction', '', '', 'Not available', '', '', 'This ultra-high resolution (12MP) fisheye camera allows monitoring of large areas which would otherwise require several cameras. It not only provides a panoramic image, but zoomed-in, detailed views as well.  It is manufactured from 316L stainless steel and so it suitable for marine and offshore environments. It comes ready for mounting and requires only a PoE network connection (or 12vdc). It is designed for use in onshore, offshore, marine and heavy industrial environments including passenger ships & commercial vessels.  ', '2048', '£1,761.28', 'ArgesMarine', '', 'AISI 316L Electro Polished Stainless Steel', '12MP resolution', '180 degree view', 'Shock and Vibration Tested', '12VDC / POE', 'IP66', '-40°C~60°C', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
